As comment 8 points out, there is a rabbit hole of missing libc routines in older version of FreeBSD.  I'm not going to chase all of that down.

@Kubilay, I'm sorry you feel that way.  But I'm doing this as a volunteer, and IMO even supporting 10.3 is generous.

I'm not going to commit this.  But anyone with a port bit that actually wants to fix this (with requisite testing) has my blessing.
